AC-03 All JSON API endpoints return Content-Type: application/json
AC-04 Successful POST returns HTTP 201; successful GET returns 200; successful DELETE returns 200 or 204
AC-05 Error responses (404, 400, 422) return a JSON body: { 'error': 'message' }
